==Finnish==
===Intransitive verb===
'''ilmestyä'''

#to [[appear]], to [[come in sight]]
#*Se ilmestyi puun takaa.
#**It came in sight behind the tree.
#to [[be issued]]
#*Lehti ilmestyy joka kuukausi.
#**The magazine is issued every month.

====Synonyms====
*(''appear'') [[tulla näkyviin]]
*(''be issued'') [[julkaista]]

